@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

### ✅ Registrar novo usuário
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "gabriel",
  "email": "gabriel@email.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 🔑 Fazer login (gera token JWT)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "gabriel",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 📋 Listar tarefas (usa token automaticamente)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### ➕ Criar nova tarefa
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Aprender Spring Boot",
  "description": "Estudar autenticação com JWT",
  "completed": false
}

### ✏️ Atualizar tarefa (exemplo ID = 1)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Aprender Spring Boot (Atualizado)",
  "description": "JWT funcionando perfeitamente",
  "completed": true
}

### ❌ Deletar tarefa (exemplo ID = 1)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
